# identity-svc (headless FastStream) — Phase 1
#
# Most settings come from common.env (POSTGRES_*, REDIS_URL, RABBITMQ_URL) and
# auth.env (JWT_SECRET_KEY, JWT_ALGORITHM, OAuth creds, SERVICE_CLIENTS/SCOPES).
# This file carries only identity-svc-specific overrides.

